edfordshire<\/a>, who provided invaluable technical support for the team throughout the sessions. Their details can be found <a title=\"University of Bedfordshire students\" href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/researchexchange\/events\/mirandanet-bett12-programme-11th-14th-january-london\/workshop-sessions-at-bett12\/university-of-bedfordshire-students\/\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Donna Burton-Wilcox Tom Rank, from NATE, talked about\u00a0Powering up English with ICT Using MindMeister The interactions in the MirandaMod and the FlashMeeting are further augmented by the use of MindMeister, a collaborative mapping tool being used to create and store &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/mirandamods-at-bett\/bett12\/improving-access-to-achievement-using-digital-technologies\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":44,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/116"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=116"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/116\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":441,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/116\/revisions\/441"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/44"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"htt